Name: MEANDERS
About the game: WELCOME TO MEANDERS! A sparkling theme park full of platform and environmental puzzles. Have fun! 40 levels of instant play with no loading times: relax or speedrun to the exit! Jump, bounce, slide, teleport! Cannons too are a totally safe mean of transportation Enjoy the company of an all-powerful AI god - Unless you find out how to destroy it Speedrun Mode & Steam Leaderboards available! Original Soundtrack both funky and soothing Use the ATOMIC STUFF to activate the insane game and visual modes!!
